Package: edgeCounter
Title: Counting edges of BAM alignment against a GRanges object
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Ye", "Yuan", , "yeyu@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9641-9102"))
Description: Given a BAM alignment file, each read pair will have two edges/ends.
    This package counts number of read pair edges that overlaps within
    each range of the 'GRanges'.
    This package contains a complete example for ATAC sequencing quantification.
License: GPL (>= 3)
